Dia. 01 Black, One Liberty Less
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black plays at 1 it is hard to expect that Black will win the capturing race.
\par If White plays the hane at 2, Black has only two while White has three liberties.
\par
\par It is easy to see that Black has \cf1\b one liberty less\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par }
